-- pd.package: Color Doc
name: fifthtry.github.io/color-doc

Color Doc is a color schemes which can be used to change color scheme of web 
packages via using `FTD` lang.

To use `color-doc` color scheme on your web package, add below into `FPM.ftd` file:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd


\-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/color-doc as colors


